		"body": "This PR fixes an issue where the left selection border was cut off in the Rich Text Editor when selecting non-editable blocks such as code blocks.\r\n\r\nThe selection outline was clipped on the left side. This change adjusts the selection styling so the border is fully visible without overlapping the text.\r\n\r\nFixes #14141\r\n",
